{
  "texts": [
    "Recent work has begun to explore the potential of LLMs for mental health applications.",
    "Studies have shown promising results in the detection of signs of depression, anxiety, and suicidal ideation from social media posts (Ma et al., 2024).",
    "The evolution of LLM capabilities has particular relevance for mental health research.",
    "Recent studies have shown that advanced LLM versions can provide human-level interpretations in qualitative coding tasks (Dunivin, 2024) and achieve accuracy comparable to mental health professionals in certain diagnostic contexts (Kim et al., 2024).",
    "When applied to qualitative analysis, LLMs have demonstrated the ability to perform various analytical approaches, including thematic analysis, content analysis, and grounded theory, as validated by human experts (Xiao et al., 2023b; Rasheed et al., 2024)."
  ]
}